# ===============================================================
# AutoPipeline — optional overrides
# ===============================================================
# You normally DON'T need this file. `npm run setup` writes the
# correct .env into each fetched app automatically:
#
#   apps/agent/.env      (all optional — LLM keys are entered in the UI)
#   apps/backend/.env    PORT=3333, AGENT_URL=http://localhost:8000
#   apps/frontend/.env   NEXT_PUBLIC_BACKEND_URL=http://localhost:3333
#
# LLM provider API keys are NOT set here. You enter them in the app's
# LLM selector at runtime (stored encrypted by the desktop shell).
